DBsheetConfig.query: SELECT T2.value Discounting, T3.value name, T1.id FROM ORE.dbo.TodaysMarketSwapIndexCurves T1 INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T2 ON T1.Discounting = T2.value INNER JOIN ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName T3 ON T1.name = T3.value

field.name: *Discounting
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value Discounting, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value

field.name: *name
field.lookup: SELECT !T!.value name, !T!.value FROM ORE.dbo.TypesIndexName !T! ORDER BY value
